    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:fountaingraceinternational@gmail.com">fountaingraceinternational@gmail.com</a></p>
    <p style="color:var(--muted)">Soon this page will include a form connected to our prayer automation.</p>
  </div>
</Base>
